title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Pick 4 1PM' game
maintext:
PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Thursday afternoon’s drawing of the Oregon Lottery’s “Pick 4 1PM” game were:
9-9-7-6
(nine, nine, seven, six)
